Darrel G. ADAMS, Warden, petitioner,
v.
Earl Eugene CANNEDY, Jr. No. 13-478. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 21, 2014.

Case below, 706 F.3d 1148.

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the *1002United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
